tip.text: Super yummy congee!
Very good Peruvian food at a down to earth place. Try the various potato appetizers like Causa
B'stilla Fassia: crispy layer of thin fyllo dough stuffed with duck breast. It's great!
Duck Liver Cromesquis with grape is so good!
Monterey Bay Squid and Pork Fried Rice is must have!
Delicious Duck Liver Cromesquis, grape, mustard seed gastrique, spicy cress!
Yummy Nutella Puff and Chocolate Almond Croissant
Decent Taiwanese Pork Chop, either with rice or in noodle soup!
Scallop Oil and Pork Dry Noodle is pretty good
Pickled Mustard Green Pork Stomach Soup!
Durian and Jasmine Tea ice cream!
I love that they serve Verve coffee!
Poached Pear Almond Tart was very good!  The young woman who worked behind the counter this afternoon was not as good
Yummy Taiwanese Sausage!  Their Sausage Burger is great!
Yummy crepes, French Onion Soup and Jeremiah's Pick Coffee!
A surprisingly good Korean place in Foster City!  Very spacious.  Great service. Free WiFi. I enjoyed their Bulgogi Tacos (with daikon wraps)!
Miso Momo (chicken thigh), marinated in miso for 3 days, is yummy!
Kimchi Natto is a good combination!
Pork Lettuce Cup is not what we have expected
Two people can share one pot!  Don't know why I didn't think of that until I saw the next table ...
Good housemade smoked trout in the salad!
Delicious Green Grape Sorbetto!
Yes the coffee is great here but do give their tea a try as well. I love their Mint Herbal Tea! 😻
Best sushi place in Milpitas!  Expect more traditional nigiri than a bunch of fusion sushi rolls
Get their house-made spinach and beet gnocchi, crispy prosciutto, creamy leek sauce!
